window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Sir Ian McKellen was the winner of the BBC Audio Drama Award 2015 for Best Actor in an Audio Drama (for Eugenie Grandet) </b></p> <p>Sir Ian McKellen reads <i>The Valley of Fear</i>, the last of Sir Arthur Conan Doyle's four Sherlock Holmes novels. </p> <p>The mystery begins with a coded warning of imminent danger, drawing the illustrious Sherlock Holmes and the faithful Dr. Watson to a secluded English country home. A trail of bewildering clues leads to sleuthing in the finest Holmesian tradition and the gripping backstory of a cult that terrorized a valley in the American West. </p> <p>First broadcast as Book at Bedtime on BBC Radio 4.</p>";